# Deploying Agents to Hostinger VPS

[x] Locate the local agent source code
[x] Determine the deployment method (SSH/SCP, Git, Docker, etc.)
[x] Connect to Hostinger VPS via SSH
[x] Install necessary dependencies on VPS (Node.js, PM2, etc.)
[x] Transfer the code or clone the repository to the VPS
[x] Configure environment variables (.env) on the VPS
[x] Start and configure the agents to run 24/7 (e.g., via PM2 or a systemd service)
[/] Verify the agents are fully operational via Telegram
